                span.firstcharacter
                  | T
                | ired of hearing or reading only bad news? The gospel of Jesus Christ is always good news!

              p
                | Here's why this is the best news you'll ever hear ...

              h2 God Loves Us 

              h3 His Love Is Unconditional
              ul
                li God is for us, not against us! 
                li God wants relationship with us.
                li God wants to be part of our daily lives.
                li God wants us to know Him personally.
                li God wants to give purpose to our lives through collaboration in His eternal plan.

              h2 God Is Our Provider

              h3 He Knows Our Needs Before We Ask
              ul
                li God is willing and able to meet our every need.
                li God wants to bless us abundantly in every area of our lives.
                li God is a loving and gracious Father.
                li God will not withhold any good thing from His children.
                li Jesus is the Good Shepherd who cares for His sheep so that they shall not want.

              h2 Jesus Is Our Healer 

              ul
                li Jesus heals all of our sicknesses, diseases and infirmities (physical and mental).
                li Jesus mends the broken-hearted and binds up their wounds.
                li Jesus restores broken relationships.
                li Jesus cleanses us from all guilt, shame, regret and condemnation.
                li Jesus breaks the chain of every addiction and wrong belief to set us free.

              h2 Jesus Is Our Peace

              ul
                li God is our protector from all evil. His angels camp around us and deliver us.
                li God is our security and refuge in times of trouble. He is our hiding place and shield.
                li Jesus casts out our every doubt and fear.
                li Jesus will never leave us nor forsake us. We need never be anxious nor afraid.
                li God is faithful and trustworthy. We can have full confidence in all His great and precious promises.

              h2 Jesus Is Our Saviour 

              ul
                li Sin separates man from God. 
                li Jesus made a way to reconcile sinful man back to God.
                li The blood of Jesus paid the ransom for the sins of the world.
                li Through faith in Jesus, all of our sins are forgiven and blotted out!
                li Man can once more enter back into full relationship with God as children of God with all of the above blessings.

              h2 Free Gift 

              p 
                | Are you ready to receive salvation as the free gift of God with all of the above blessings?

